57.7	Urbanization	Urbanization	Urbanization, urbanisation or urban drift is the physical growth of urban areas as a result of global change. The United Nations projected that half of the world's population would live in urban areas at the end of 2008.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/LosAngeles05.jpg/250px-LosAngeles05.jpg
